<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa thangthat hi, a nuam i a hman
 Chun le zan in, Bawipa thangthat tuah
 Thangthat a duhmi, kan Pathian a si
 Thangthat Bawipa.

[C1]
   Zing can ah, Chun can ah, zan can zongah
   Bawipa cu, thangthat tuah, lung lawm in,
   Bawipa fale nih, Bawipa thangthat u, a men.

[V2]
 Kan chungkhar tlingin, lawmhnak zaihla he
 Bawipa hmaiah kun in bia u sih
 Kan chungkhar damnak, kan thluachuah hram cu
 Thangthat zaihla.

[V3]
 Kan taksa thinlung, kan thlarau caah
 Lawmhnak sitha Bawipa thangthat u
 Van khi a ser I, Vawlei kha a uk
 Bawipa thangthat.</lyrics>
<title>BAWIPA THANGTHAT A NUAM</title>
</song>